---
/**
 * Hero – landing redesign 2026-05-09 (handoff).
 * Layout: editorial 2-column grid. Lewy: section-index + eyebrow,
 * display-xxl headline, subhead (max 520px), 2 CTAs.
 * Prawy: violet atmosphere card – 3-stop radial + ::before inner-light overlay.
 */
---

<section class="hero-section" id="home">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <!-- LEFT: copy stack -->
      <div class="hero-left">
        <div class="hero-meta">
          <span class="section-index">S/01</span>
          <span class="eyebrow">Generative Engine Optimization</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="display-xxl hero-headline">
          Sprawdź, co ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini i <span class="hero-mobile-break" aria-hidden="true"
          ></span>Perplexity mówią o&nbsp;<span class="accent">Twojej marce</span>.
        </h1>

        <p class="subhead hero-sub">
          Sprawdź już teraz, czy AI poleca Twoją markę, czy boty AI mają dostęp do&nbsp;Twojej
          strony i&nbsp;jak zoptymalizować swój content, aby był cytowany przez wyszukiwarki AI.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a class="btn-primary" href="#audyty" aria-label="Uruchom darmowe testy widoczności AI">
            Uruchom darmowe testy
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
          <a
            class="btn-secondary"
            href="/kontakt/?type=full-report"
            aria-label="Zamów pełny raport GEO"
          >
            Zamów pełny raport
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT: violet atmosphere card -->
      <article class="hero-card on-gradient">
        <span class="hero-card-eyebrow">Ewolucja tradycyjnego SEO</span>
        <p class="hero-card-quote">
          AI zmienia wyszukiwarki w&nbsp;<em>silniki odpowiedzi</em>, które eliminują konieczność
          przeklikiwania się przez wyniki. Marki pominięte przez ChatGPT, Claude czy Perplexity
          po&nbsp;prostu <em>przestają istnieć</em> w&nbsp;decyzji konsumenta.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-card-meta">
          <span>Cytowania zamiast pozycji</span>
          <span>SEO + GEO</span>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background:
      radial-gradient(
        circle at 13% 12%,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent-blue) 18%, transparent) 0%,
        transparent 30%
      ),
      radial-gradient(circle at 88% 20%, rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.18) 0%, transparent 32%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-surface-1) 0%, var(--bg-canvas) 88%);
    padding: 80px 0 96px;
  }

  .hero-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(var(--hairline-soft) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, var(--hairline-soft) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 64px 64px;
    mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.13), transparent 66%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-grid {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  @media (min-width: 980px) {
    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr) minmax(440px, 0.95fr);
      gap: 72px;
    }
  }

  .hero-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-meta .eyebrow {
    font-family: ui-monospace, 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .hero-meta .eyebrow::before {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
  }

  /* Display headline – clamp + relative tracking (handoff) */
  .hero-headline {
    max-width: 14.5ch;
    text-wrap: pretty;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .hero-mobile-break {
    white-space: normal;
  }

  .hero-mobile-break::after {
    content: ' ';
  }

  /* Inline accent (sky) na "Twojej marce" – z .accent (Theme.css) */

  .hero-sub {
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0;
    /* na hero kluczowy tekst – ink, nie ink-muted (zgodnie z feedbackiem) */
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 4px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero-section {
      padding: 72px 0 80px;
    }

    .hero-left {
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .hero-headline {
      max-width: 100%;
      text-wrap: balance;
    }

    .hero-mobile-break {
      display: block;
    }

    .hero-mobile-break::after {
      content: '';
    }

    .hero-sub {
      max-width: 100%;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 340px;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .hero-cta .btn-primary,
    .hero-cta .btn-secondary {
      width: 100%;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .hero-card {
      min-height: 320px;
      padding: 28px;
      border-radius: var(--r-xl);
    }
  }

  /* ============================================================
     Hero atmosphere card – violet 3-stop radial + ::before overlay
     ============================================================ */

  .hero-card {
    background-color: #2a2678;
    background-image: var(--grad-violet);
    border-radius: var(--r-xxl);
    padding: 36px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    min-height: 380px;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px -28px rgba(110, 40, 240, 0.55);
  }

  .hero-card-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .hero-card-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .hero-card-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2vw, 30px);
    line-height: 1.18;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0;
    /* OpenType variants Inter – tu używamy display, więc pomijamy */
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .hero-card-quote em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .hero-card-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
</style>
